character.name:
Isometric pixel art ruby lion monster for a 2D RPG game

Fantasy lion creature made of ruby and red crystal, not realistic.

Strong muscular body with crystal plates embedded in the skin, glowing red highlights.

Large majestic mane made of faceted ruby crystals, sharp and angular shapes.

Eyes glowing bright red, intimidating and powerful presence.

Clawed paws with crystal claws, tail ending in a large ruby crystal.

Isometric 3/4 top-down view, aligned for 64x32 isometric grid.

Designed as a game enemy / mini-boss, clear readable silhouette.

Pixel art style, sharp pixels, no blur, no smooth gradients.

Limited color palette (reds, dark crimson, subtle shadows).

Hand-crafted pixel shading, exaggerated fantasy proportions.

Neutral or transparent background, no ground, no characters, no UI.

Style inspired by Dofus 1.29, classic fantasy RPG monsters.
